reviewText: This is the most important health information you will ever learn. I am a Health Coach and counselor, I really appreciate this form of easy educational products!! I recommend them to everyone!

This is truly a life changing series. It is extremely well presented and informative. For anyone interested in,a raw food living food diet it is a must. What I especially like about it is that it you gain so much more information to enhance your health than you do in a book.
